nodes.label: In this time of exam-stress_ it_s easy to forget about what_s really important: Christmas spirit and playing games! So join us this friday along with Gateway_ ITU LAN_ and StupIT_ have a beer_ some æbleskiver_ and enjoy the friday in good company <3

Alright guys_ it_s getting colder outside_ and the snow is about to fall. In ScrollBar_ we_ll guarantee you that it will fall this friday! How do we know that? Because it_s J-Day!! Tuborg is releasing their Julebryg_ and we_ll grasp the opportunity to have one hell of a party. So be sure to tell your friends_ come on down_ and enjoy this very special tradition with us <3

Alright guys and gals! The fall break is over_ Christmas break is in sight – and we’ve paved the whole way with awesome parties for you all!  This Friday (the 23rd) the LAN-guys are joining the party-planning team and doing some awesome tournaments open for everyone and with awesome prizes_ so be sure to check it out! Here: https://www.facebook.com/events/1476745142648528/  Next week_ we’ll of course celebrate Halloween in true scary ScrollBar style with costume-discounts and prizes for both the best male costume_ and the best female costume! So get out your scariest gear_ and get ready for a fright-fest – nerdy ITU-style! Check the event out here: https://www.facebook.com/events/863218880433744/  And of course we also have both J-day and our biannual foosball tournament coming up_ and so much more!  Be sure to subscribe to our events to stay in the loop – and we’ll be sure to keep you entertained all the way to Christmas!  ScrollBar loves you <3

Ladies and gentlemen! Tomorrow is the infamous Annual Party!! This means that this is the one time of year that you will need a TICKET to get in to ScrollBar_ and it means that we will not open until 6 pm. This also means_ however_ that we will have one hell of a party!!  We can_t wait to see you! <3

In a little bit_ we_ll open our doors for another chill friday bar :) So come on down when you_re done with classes and your serious academic work_ and join us in celebrating that it_s finally friday!   Oh_ and remember: ScrollBar loves you <3

Hey guys! It_s come to our attention that there_s been some confusion as to where to send your applications. The correct email address is JOIN@SCROLLBAR.DK ! If you_ve sent it to another address_ please send it to us at the correct one_ or we won_t be able to read it.  Sorry about the confusion_ and remember: ScrollBar loves you! <3

Remember that you still have some time if you want to join ScrollBar!  We_re accepting applications until sunday at midnight_ so hurry up and show us why we need you as part of our family by sending your application to join@ScrollBar.dk! If you have any questions you can go to www.scrollbar.dk/join_ or stop by the bar today and talk to your favourite tenders - we_re open until 2am as usual :)  Oh_ and remember: ScrollBar loves you <3

Do you wanna know what_s going on in ScrollBar RIGHT NOW?  Follow us on Snapchat to see what_s up during parties_ and maybe catch some behind the scenes snapshots during the week! Go to snapchat and add ScrollBar to your contacts - you won_t regret it ;)  <3

The start of the semester is upon us!! The clearest indication of the end of summer is the intro party_ and boy did we have one hell of a party! This Friday all the new students at ITU were welcomed with open arms and open beer-taps_ and boy could they party!  They emptied the bar and showed us what to expect for the rest of the semester_ so next Friday we will refill our stock and prepare ourselves for what will happen when they join the rest of you for our massive Back 2 School party!! We_re looking forward to seeing you again; be it in front of or behind the bar.   ScrollBar loves you <3

Summer is over us_ and all the student initiatives are getting ready to make next semester even more awesome for you!  One of them is Analog_ who is finally getting ready for its big move into new a new and bigger setting! Help them make the best of their new locale by submitting your ideas right here on this link :) (more info after the jump)

True to tradition_ we_ll be open on the last day of hand-ins!  (We are aware that some of you cool kids may have later deadlines_ but come on_ we just really want an excuse to get drunk)  ScrollBar loves you! <3

Hey guys! Remember that ScrollBar will be open today from 3pm! :) So if you need a break from all of the hard work that we know you_re doing_ stop by for a cold brew :) Today is also the final day of our DrinkBattle_ where the drinks _C-NotSo-#_ and _Half-Life 3_ will be competing to become the champion of drinks!!   We hope to see you there_ and always remember: ScrollBar loves you <3

The semester is coming to an end_ and ScrollBar is getting ready to close down for the summer. BUT! Before that happens_ we have some awesome parties in store for you guys:  May 1st - We_ll be closed_ but maybe we_ll see some of you in Fælledparken? May 8th - BBQ: You bring the meat_ we_ll bring the fire! ( https://www.facebook.com/events/831964293544665/ ) May 15th - Last friday bar of the semester.  May 20th - Hand-in bar!  Stay tuned for more info_ and remember: ScrollBar loves you <3

Hey guys_ are you ready for summer? We sure are!  And that_s why_ this friday_ we_ve once again teamed up with Grundejerforeningen Ørestad Universitetskvarter to have one hell of a beach party! We_ll have awesome dj_s and a 2 for 1 deal on Corona!  Head on over to this link for more info:  https://www.facebook.com/events/1439101153049742/  See you all on friday_ and remember: ScrollBar loves you <3
Thank you all so much for celebrating our birthday with us! ScrollBar loves you <3

After what has seemed like an eternity_ we can finally give you a present that should make things a whole lot easier for you guys this coming Friday and in general! We can now accept several different card types as listed here below :)

Ladies and gentlemen! I hope you_re all excited for Friday! All of us in the bar have been looking forward to this particular party for several months and we_re basically about to explode with our pent up excitement ;)  Now_ this isn_t a party to pat ourselves on our backs - it_s to celebrate something amazing that happened way back in 2004 (legends say even earlier): the start of ScrollBar. This includes every tender who ever served a drink since then_ and every student who drank a drink since then!  So remember to join us in celebrating the awesome space and concept now known as ScrollBar this Friday!  On behalf of everyone in ScrollBar_ we look forward to seeing you :) Malik Chairman

Our birthday is coming up_ so we wanna give you a little something to celebrate! We_re having a scavenger-hunt on our Instagram_ where you can win drink-tickets for our birthday party!! So head on over to Instagram and find us @ScrollBarITU to see more <3
Join us for a drink this friday! We_ll be closed for easter next week_ so don_t miss this chance to get your ScrollBar fix ;) <3

Scrollbar loves you almost 1.000.000 times! That_s how much turnover ScrollBar had in 2014. And for that we are so grateful!  We strive to give the best combination of a well-equipped bar with a top-notch atmosphere in combination with student friendly prices.  With all you party people choosing to spend so much time with us_ it gives us the opportunities to enhance the ScrollBar feeling even more. Last year we bought and replaced equipment for 60.000 kr. an all time high_ but also things that were really needed. And we are going to spend the same or more in 2015.  This year forward we are committing 20.000_- to the SAF pool in order to help new and old initiatives thrive here at ITU. This is actually more money than our surplus last year (~18.500).  We are telling you this so you know that we really want to give money back to the student environment of ITU.   So if you want a share of that piece_ head over to  foundation.scrollbar.dk and read up on how to apply.  And remember: You are the reason why we exist_ why the friday bars are so awesome_ why we have money to give back. ScrollBar loves you <3

Did you know that ScrollBar is getting old? In fact_ this spring the bar is 11 years old!  We are of course going to celebrate_ so mark your calendars for the 10th of April!! All we can tell you for now is that it’s gonna be big_ it’s gonna be awesome_ and we hope to see you all there!  Oh_ and remember; ScrollBar loves you <3

***Do you need money??***  Got a good idea to a project for the students here at ITU?  Or would you just love to see Mads Tofte in a panda costume?  And are you lacking the funds for the project? Then look no further! Every semester_ ScrollBar will contribute 10.000 kr to student initiatives at and around ITU.  ScrollBar is finally making money_ so we decided that the money we made should go back to you_ the students at ITU! The money is for ITU students and ITU students only.   So are you up for making a board game section in Analog_ but lack the games? Or wanna have a wednesday swing dance club_ but need a teacher? Then look no further!  For more information on how to apply go to foundation.ScrollBar.dk  And remember_ all of this is because you are so very good at getting your drink on and for that ScrollBar loves you!
Saint Patrick_s Day is upon us! Come by this friday and join us for a Guinness and a good time <3
Do you like Garage as much as we do? Come by friday and show the looooooove! <3
Remember that the deadline for signups for the Foosball tournament is tonight!! We can_t wait to see you all there <3

Dear fellow students!  Now is your chance to decide what drinks or shots ScrollBar will serve in the future! For the first time ever_ ScrollBar is hosting a drinks battle and we want you to be part of it!  It_s simple: If you have a drink or shot that you think we should serve_ simply submit it. We_ll then have all submissions compete in classic tournament style_ and make our lovely guests decide which is the best one. The winner will receive eternal fame and glory_ a special prize_ and a permanent spot on the ScrollBar menu! (no fame or glory guaranteed).  So what are you waiting for? Head over to www.ScrollBar.dk/drinkbattle to participate.  ScrollBar loves you <3

Ladies and gentlemen! Friday is coming up_ and that means beer_ drinks_ and good times :) This week_ it also means that you all get to see what stupIT has been working on for you guys!   So stop by for an afternoon beer when we open @3pm_ and stick around for the big reveal @9pm!! :)  In other news: The bi-annual ScrollBar foosball tournament is next friday(the 6th)_ so gather your teams and stay tuned for more info :)  And always remember: ScrollBar loves you! <3
Just over an hour and a half left to apply!! Go to ScrollBar.dk/apply if you have any doubts_ and just send off that application!  <3

***Application deadline is closing in***  Hey everyone_ remember that tomorrow is the last day to send in your applications to join ScrollBar!! We(the board) are very excited to go through the applications and choose who gets to be part of the world_s best bartending family_ and all the members are just itching to write out recommendations to help us choose! So don_t hesitate: just send it in_ and then dress up and come party with us tonight!  Love_  Ditte_ PR  Ps: ScrollBar loves you! <3

Fastelavn falls early this year_ but we hope you_re ready! We_re celebrating this friday the 13th_ but don_t worry - you don_t have to be scary! So dig up your most awesome costume_ and join the fun :)  And remember: ScrollBar loves you <3
Hey everyone!! Remember that tomorrow is the day of our infamous meet n_ greet! We hope to see you all there <3

Welcome back everyone! We hope you’re all ready to start the new semester_ and we can’t wait to see y’all soon!! Tonight our tenders are getting back in business welcoming the new masters students_ serving the OpenITU crowd in atrium_ and from 8:30pm we will be open to anyone wishing to get their drink on :)  As always_ the first real party of the semester is the (in)famous back to school party_ and it’s sure to be one hell of a night! Hopefully you’re as excited as we are_ so grab your friends_ and we’ll be seeing you!  Xx And remember: ScrollBar loves you <3

Lovely people! Thanks for a wunderbar semester. It_s been the best for Scrollbar ever! Today the members agreed to build a mobile bar to make it possible to serve you drinks in the atrium or outside on the warm summer nights. So no more waiting a loooong while for your favorite drinks :) We are a long way from making this a reality_ but we want to let you all know what we are doing to make this bar the best student bar possible. From all of us_ to all of you: Scrollbar Loves You <3

Hey you awesome paper-writing people!   ScrollBar will not be open today due to this crazy paper-writing period.  But this means that the hand-in bar on wednesday will be so much needed. Come by and celebrate the last the beginning of your christmas vacation!  https://www.facebook.com/events/539509102818928/?ref=22

To all of you who are struggling with your hand-in for tomorrow … Remember that there is light in the end of the tunnel_ and it will be served in ScrollBar tomorrow from 2pm.   Come by and get a well deserved cold beverage! - Those who aren_t struggling are welcome as well :)
Come by and get a beer tomorrow!

A big thanks for a great evening last Friday!  We will once more like to congratulate the winners of the Bi-Annual Foosball Tournament Aslak Vanggaard & Peter Bindslev!  We can_t wait to see all of you later today!
If you want to be a part of the Foosball Tournament on Friday_ tonight at midnight is the last chance for the sign-up!  You can find the link in the event:

Hey peeps_ We have some _old_ ITU students coming by on Friday searching for a new web developer/RoR developer to join their team.  They will do some kind of informal job interviews_ where they will buy beer to people who are interested in joining their team.
We have the bi-annual Foosball Tournament on Friday - have you signed up? :)
Have you seen the crazy pictures from the Laser Rave last Friday?

ScrollBar is having A LOT OF guests these days_ and we couldn_t be happier about you guys enjoying ScrollBar as much as we do. From us to you: Thanks! :-)  However_ a lot of you may have experienced lately that you have had to wait a long time being served. So please hear us out here: 1) We are aware of the issue_ and we_re very sorry for you awesome ones having to wait.  2) We_re doing something about it_ but we can_t have it ready for this semester_ but we_re aiming for the very start of next semester. As for what that _something_ is_ we can_t go into specifics here_ but we do realize that the current mainbar can _only do so much_ and we simply need more space_ i.e. an extra bar to relieve bottleneck-issues and pressure from the mainbar. Whether that extra bar be a full-blown bar serving all the stuff you can also have in the current bar_ or only serving a reduced _menu_ has not been decided on as of yet.   So_ that was a just a quick update. Rest assured_ that we see your pain_ but please bare with us and hang on a little while longer. We are on it_ and doing our best_ so you can soon have an even better experience in ScrollBar.  Again_ we_re thrilled you seem to be liking ScrollBar as much as we do - we_ll do our best to keep it that way.   - ScrollBar
